metadata.name: Rekt Muppets #1
metadata.description: “Yes it’s 'Rekt Muppets' – an NFT collection that tells the raw tale of retail traders who got rekt by PEPE and other fly by night MEME tokens. These frog like rekt figurine pfp’s have all felt the burn of diving headfirst into these meme coins, only to lose it all. This collection puts a face to the ups and downs of crypto trading, with a focus on the moments when things go sideways. It's a lighthearted take on the trials and tribulations of the crypto space, offering a visual representation of the risks and rewards of chasing the next big coin. 'Rekt Muppets' – where art meets the reality of getting rekt.”
